<br>
When young (and not-so-young) people use the word 'fag', what they mean is, 'idiot' or something along those lines.  <br>
<br>
I'm trying to show that it's NOT ok to casually use that word.  Think about it, if you were in a room full of adults at work, and they were all bitching about an annoying coworker, would you really just shoot off, &quot;yeah he's such a fag&quot;?  <br>
<br>
You also prove my point.  People use it completely unaware of the impact it has on other people and society.  It might not change the world, but you have to start somewhere. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/udulyendetrimental.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DulyenDetrimental</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 340<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(7/3/02 1:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> o3w3l</span><hr size=1> Well uhm ok. Last night my friends had to wait an hour before picking me up after work. We close at 7p.m. and i got out at 8:30 , because of one of my co-workers. When I got off I said yeah hes a <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> fag</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> .<br>
